                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Activation cross section was measured between 11 and 15",
                "MeV with 0.5 MeV steps.",
                "Irradiation was made with 0.5puA beam for 3 and 18h.",
                "Beam intensity was controlled by measuring the",
                "backscattered alpha particles at 165 degree backward.",
                "Gamma measurements started about 1h after end of",
                "irradiation in a close measuring geometry. True",
                "coincidence summing effect was estimated and corrected."
              ]
            }
          ],
